#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/security-jwt.adoc:206
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/security-jwt.adoc:493
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/security-jwt.adoc:634
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"@Path(\"/secured\")\n"
"@RequestScoped\n"
"public class TokenSecuredResource {\n"
